summary: A collection of high quality Skyrim wallpapers and screenshots.
descriptionHtml:
[CENTER][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=6][U][COLOR=#0070c0]S[/COLOR][COLOR=#0070c0]oluti0ni[/COLOR][COLOR=#00b0f0]9[/COLOR][COLOR=#0070c0]e\'s HQ Skyrim Wallpaper Packs[/COLOR][/U][/SIZE][/FONT][/CENTER][CENTER][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=6][COLOR=#0070c0]
[/COLOR][/SIZE][/FONT][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=5][IMG]http://i1082.photobucket.com/albums/j363/solutioni9e/10293995833_be8beba211_c_zps39eb48ac.jpg[/IMG][/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]
[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2][IMG]http://i1082.photobucket.com/albums/j363/solutioni9e/10393807336_0145fb531e_c_zps7661b149.jpg[/IMG][/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]
[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2][IMG]http://i1082.photobucket.com/albums/j363/solutioni9e/10355415293_bdcbb976de_c_zps26531061.jpg[/IMG][/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]
[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]This is a collection of my high quality Skyrim screenshots/wallpapers. The images are all captured and uploaded by me. They have NOT been post-processed, Photoshopped or enhanced in any way (apart from using ENB). They are available in 1920x1080 resolution for widescreen monitors and 1600x900 standard screen formats only. So, what\'s with the black bars on the top and bottom of most of my images? They are called \"vignettes\". All my images contain it - I think it adds a nice, movie-like effect and atmosphere to all my shots :] (Sorry, I can\'t remove it!)[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]
[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]These images are by no means vanilla. I\'ve used the True Vision and Mistveil \'Autumn\' ENBs. I use roughly 120 mods that enhance textures.[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]
[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]Creating mods is beyond my abilities - in fact, this is an ode to all the wonderful modders and tweakers out there! These images (and many more) are a thank you to the entire modding community![/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]
[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2][B][I]Thank you for downloading!!![/I][/B][/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]- Soluti0ni9e[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]
[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2].[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2].[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2].[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]
[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]Pack A contains images using the Mistveil ENB.[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]Pack B contains images using the True Vision ENB.[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]
[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2][I]These packs will be updated frequently![/I][/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2][I]
[/I][/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2][I][IMG]http://i1082.photobucket.com/albums/j363/solutioni9e/10278030345_83edeec4f5_c_zps41c42832.jpg[/IMG][/I][/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]
[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2].[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2].[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2].[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=4]For more images, check out my [URL=http://www.flickr.com/photos/solutioni9e/]Flickr[/URL] , [URL=http://soluti0ni9e.tumblr.com/]Tumblr[/URL] or [URL=http://soluti0ni9e.deviantart.com/]Deviant Art[/URL] site![/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]

[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=4]FAQ[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]
[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]- Can I use these images elsewhere?[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]NO. You can use them for your personal wallpaper only. I don\'t want to see these being uploaded to other sites![/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]
[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]- Can I use these images for my mods page?[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]Yes, but please send me a message stating you would like do so :)[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]
[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]- What mods/tweaks do you use?[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]See my recommended mods list a bit further down this page.[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]
[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]- What image capturing software do you use?[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]I use a nifty little program called [URL=http://www.fraps.com/]FRAPS[/URL]. This program is to be started before you run your game and allows you to take high quality screenshots while in game. No more using Steam\'s crappy in-game F12 snapshot![/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]
[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]- What hardware do you run?[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]Intel i5-2500k CPU @ 3.70 GHz Turbo Boost[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]ASRock P67 Extreme4 Gen3 Mobo[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]8GB G.Skill Ripjaws [/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]WD Black 750GB 7200 RPM HDD[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]PNY XLR8 GeForce GTX 660 Ti Fermi 2GB GDDR5 GFX Card[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]23.5\" ASUS LCD Monitor[/SIZE][/FONT][/COLOR][/CENTER][CENTER][COLOR=#0070c0][FONT=Century Gothic][SIZE=2]
